    "content": "<p>The shaded region is the solution set of the inequalities</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1ltcftw51/42ebd4ea-9bea-4195-aeea-5c041685ae8d/33f80250-d9df-11ee-9fe4-1197aa8394ec/file-1ltcftw52.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1ltcftw51/42ebd4ea-9bea-4195-aeea-5c041685ae8d/33f80250-d9df-11ee-9fe4-1197aa8394ec/file-1ltcftw52.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2021 Mathematics - Linear Programming Question 11 English\"></p>",
